      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8513540824260608
    m_Localized: Turbo Turtle loses battery over time and when using its powers.
      Collecting Suns lets it stay alive and avoid running out!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73353655758848
    m_Localized: "With 3 suns, a player can bring back a defeated flower \nby getting
      close and holding the revive button."
