  - m_Id: 417629656854528
    m_Localized: 'Turbo Turtle curls into its shell and spins, then bursts forward
      when the button is released.


      Level 1: 1s charge

      Level 2: 1.5s
      charge

      (can break some obstacles and stuns flowers)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
